    <h2 class="section-title">What we do for griddles, and what we don't.</h2>

    <p><strong>We service:</strong></p>
    <ul class="bullet-list">
      <li>Gas commercial griddles (Vulcan VCRG, Garland ED, Star-Max, Keating Miraclean, Bakers Pride XX)</li>
      <li>Electric griddles (Wells G series specialty)</li>
      <li>Single-zone and multi-zone configurations 24 to 72 inch widths</li>
      <li>Steel plate and chrome plate (Keating Miraclean) griddles</li>
      <li>Thermostat calibration with certified equipment</li>
      <li>Igniter, thermocouple replacement</li>
      <li>Multi-zone wiring and controller diagnosis</li>
      <li>Burner head cleaning</li>
      <li>Drip tray drain clearing</li>
      <li>Heating element replacement (electric)</li>
