    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong></p>
    <ul class="bullet-list">
      <li>Plate resurfacing (specialty trade, heavy-duty plate refinishing requires industrial machine grinding equipment)</li>
      <li>Plate replacement (3/4 to 1 inch thick steel plates require specialty fabrication)</li>
      <li>New griddle installation (specialty installer trade, gas line plus electrical engineering)</li>
      <li>Combination griddle/range integrated units, see <a href="/commercial/range-repair/">commercial range repair</a> for ranges with integrated griddle module</li>
