    <p class="section-number">07 · Related equipment</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Griddles often pair with adjacent commercial cooking equipment.</h2>

    <p>If your operation has a Vulcan range with integrated griddle module (VR-36-1G24 configuration), see <a href="/brands/vulcan-range-repair/">Vulcan range repair</a>. Garland Master Series ranges with griddle integration: <a href="/brands/garland-range-repair/">Garland range repair</a>. Vulcan brand hub for full Vulcan equipment catalog: <a href="/brands/vulcan/">Vulcan</a>.</p>

